soccer.common

Interface TOS_AgentConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TOS_Constants

    public interface TOS_AgentConstants
    This class must be the only place for keeping all TOS player agent final constants. Using locally defined public static constants in other classes is still allowed, yet not recommended. Rather, it is recommended creating inherited interfaces for this interface if new constants are introduced or existing ones overridden.
    Author:
    vkyrylov (2010)
